oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Mule Day parade
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of people in the streets of Columbia for the Mule Day parade. A group of girls sit on a structure resembling a parade float. A man tends to a mule that is wearing a crown, on, left.
